data_table.description: Vascular Morphology Measurements from CT Lung Image (Round 2), Offspring, Generation 3, Omni 1, and Omni 2, 2008-2011. This dataset contains vasculature measurements of the whole lung from the second round CT scans with the primary goal of accessing coronary artery calcification.

variable.description: Unique study participant identification number

variable.name: IDTYPE
variable.description: Framingham Heart Study cohort identifier
